      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PATRIOT NIAMH (4) stalked the lead from the inside draw before finishing second last start (22.24) at this track in Grade 5 over 390m. Capable of going well again. GAS LANTERN (6) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 2.5 lengths at this track in a handy 22.31 beating Vinny Dewalt. Shapes as a top winning chance on latest effort. PAW MISSY (1) turned in a plain effort last time when sixth at Horsham over 410m behind Paw Olympus (23.76) in a Mix 3/4. Placed at her previous run. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and two minor placings from five starts. Great chance to atone. PAW OPPA (2) can measure up with the right run.",
